messages.text: Hi. Sorry to bother you, but I noticed that you've been playing this game a bit. Hopefully that means you like it. Either way, I would really appreciate some feedback to help me make it better. Send an email (commissioner@basketball-gm.com) or join the discussion on Reddit or Discord.

This year: Bad.

Overall: It's too early to judge you.

Hopefully you'll win some more games next season. And try to make some more money too!
